    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it doesn't feel like a relief though. it just feels heavy. like the fog is so thick it's actually suffocating me. looking at the drop-off from the cliff, it's the only thing that looks clear. everything else is just... blur and exhaustion. it feels like this is where the story was always supposed to end.",
